otional products packaging fulfillment  distribution testimonials portfolio resources reference materials contact send a file feedback survey employment opportunities b promo shop wide format posters to custom folios and pens annual investors meeting — centerbridge partners centerbridge partners lp is a private investment firm with offices in new york and london the firm focuses on private equity  credit investments each year they hold a multiday investor gathering to detail their performance and provide a roadmap for their future centerbridge needed a partner that could handle all of their printing needs — they found that partner in b squared running an event of this size is not easy in fact we start planning and coordinating efforts up to a year in advance the event requires multiple items from all corners of the services that we offer from coordination of invitation and registration materials to all signage and collateral used at the onsite meeting to dayof registration and ondemand printing services if we had to choose a favorite item we’d have to choose the thing that every attendee carries with them a custom turnededge capacity folio this folio contains important event information notepads and a branded pen the folio acts as a guide for them at the event and the branded pen acts a reminder of centerbridge partners long after the event is over we’re proud of our partnership with centerbridge partners and the success of the annual investors meeting we also think it’s pretty cool that all of the materials from the pens to the wide format posters were created in our shop  west th street th floor new york ny  phone   fax   email infobsqucom designed by pidalia centerbridge partners acquire industrial container services llc from aurora capital group  the business journals menu select a city national albany albuquerque atlanta austin baltimore birmingham boston buffalo charlotte chicago cincinnati columbus dallas dayton denver greensborowinstonsalem honolulu houston 